{"tid":976344,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港航空傳引資 洽國泰股權合作","createTime":"2019-01-10T10:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T15:17:41.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a15275658a83a3efd124fdb44166045ab0bbae5a","tid":976344,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/01/10/2035519_c9bce50d1f0f99181adeed1197c663fd_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F01%2F10%2F2035519_c9bce50d1f0f99181adeed1197c663fd_320.jpg&h=546d7a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地《第一財經》引述消息稱，海航集團旗下香港航空正與多方面洽談引資，其中包括國泰航空(00293)。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，港航與國泰洽談內容包括網絡協調、股權合作等一系列層面。<br />\n<br />\n報道又稱，海航正研究加入國際航空聯盟，港航與國泰之後關係，將是海航未來要加入哪家國際航空聯盟的重要決定因素。"},{"pid":"c99b527b6ae4c1562c0596a8a7fec7c09166ecbc","tid":976344,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"聽日千升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127aaef5fdb112d2076592338b09f705fab6f6af","tid":976344,"uid":56698,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:07:26.000Z","msg":"係就好 香港個名畀太古好過"},{"pid":"2accb94f660b3c81e0f4619ea4e1b2d902a44e38","tid":976344,"uid":205915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"會唔會入埋 one world <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c486f0964d5d8d178f9434090d82319fe7ba7eb6","tid":976344,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"搞下搞下香港遲早得返一間airline"},{"pid":"5fb0d3cad44df8d7e98b2ae06d8483991bd9e248","tid":976344,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"HAS食完HIAS再食HAGSL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa65561aa71eb80a6be0c2e658bd8e42d4cea70","tid":976344,"uid"